text: Aitovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Urshakbashkaramalinsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 121 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 44 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 13 km from Urshakbashkaramaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Aitovo, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
